}}</ref> Southern is a [[dry campus]],<ref name="al">{{cite web|title=Southern Adventist University {{!}} Campus Information and Services|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/southern-adventist-3518/campus-info|publisher=''[[U.S. News and World Report]]''|accessdate=2011-04-22}}</ref> as the Adventist Church opposes the use of alcohol.<ref>{{Cite web 
|url=http://www.sdada.org/aboutsda.htm
|title=About Seventh-day Adventists
|publisher=Seventh-day Adventist Dietetic Association
|accessdate=2011-11-15
